            <para>MaxxForce&#8482;DT, 9, and 10 engines are available in various front cover and cooling system
                configurations. Engines are available with or without a power takeoff (PTO) adaptor attachment on the
                front cover. Numerous spin-on and Horton DriveMaster&#174; fan drive configurations are available.
                Engines can be equipped with one, two, or no Freon&#174; compressor. Several water outlet tubes are also
                used. See
                <hotlnk document="eges3351_17.xml" xrefid="s0124">Engine Cooling System</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="s0124"/>
                for additional details.
            </para>
